name: Durable Tim (SethDossett)
description:
Disclaimer: If Game runs too slow in browser, download Windows build.

GameDev.tv Game Jam 2022

Theme: "Death is Only The Beginning"

Developers:  Gabriel Contreras from Academy of Games and Seth Dossett

Tim is an unnaturally durable dude. The government is using him for testing. You work for the government, don't let us down.

Press space to jump from the plane. Use your mouse and keyboard to move around. Kill Tim and see What Happens. After you die don't touch the ground.
